<!--Tengyō Rebellion of the Dewa Fusho--> [[Category:10th-century battles]] [[Category:Japan in 939]] [[Category:Incidents of the Heian period]] [[Category:Battles of the Heian period]] [[Category:Ezo]] [[Category:Ezo]] <!--jawiki derived wikidata interwikis--> [[Category:qq]]
